										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="4">胃是我们身体中非常重要的一个消化吸收器官，俗话说十人九胃，这句话想表达的意思是，每10个人当中可能会有9个人存在胃部方面的状况。</p>
<p data-track="5">研究数据显示，近几年患胃病的人的确越来越多，也让人们感觉到非常担忧，害怕自己患上胃部疾病不自知。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-610" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/7ed0c26cc2507ad310a41ed21a4797c8-1024x536.jpg" width="1024" height="536" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/7ed0c26cc2507ad310a41ed21a4797c8-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/7ed0c26cc2507ad310a41ed21a4797c8-300x157.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/7ed0c26cc2507ad310a41ed21a4797c8-768x402.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/7ed0c26cc2507ad310a41ed21a4797c8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">几乎所有的身体疾病出现之前，身体都会提前通风报信，只是有些时候人们并没有关注身体的异常信号。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="7">胃部功能异常，会有哪些典型信号？</h1>
<ul>
<li data-track="8"><strong>疼痛</strong></li>
</ul>
<p data-track="9">人们常说肝是哑巴，胃是喇叭。</p>
<p data-track="10">当肝脏功能出现异常的时候，或许不会有明显的疼痛感，但是胃部出现了状况就会有剧烈的疼痛感。</p>
<p data-track="11">所以疼痛是典型的胃病信号，因此也提醒大家平时多关注一下胃部的状况，如果一段时间内感觉胃部疼痛的情况非常明显的话，最好要提高警惕。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-611" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/5d6ee2efcdefdca6ff2650a18314e468.jpg" width="1000" height="668" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/5d6ee2efcdefdca6ff2650a18314e468.jpg 1000w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/5d6ee2efcdefdca6ff2650a18314e468-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/5d6ee2efcdefdca6ff2650a18314e468-768x513.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<ul>
<li data-track="12"><strong>睡眠质量变差</strong></li>
</ul>
<p data-track="13">中医认为胃不和，则卧不安，也就是说胃部功能不太好会影响到正常的睡眠，因此通过观察睡眠质量也能够判断出胃部的状况。</p>
<p data-track="14">如果一段时间内睡眠质量明显受到了影响，并且也常常会伴随失眠多梦的情况，那么就要多加注意，必要的话也应该及时去医院检查一下胃部。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-612" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/03f60203fa8bcdb39f4e3b644cf8786f-1024x410.jpg" width="1024" height="410" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/03f60203fa8bcdb39f4e3b644cf8786f-1024x410.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/03f60203fa8bcdb39f4e3b644cf8786f-300x120.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/03f60203fa8bcdb39f4e3b644cf8786f-768x307.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/03f60203fa8bcdb39f4e3b644cf8786f.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<ul>
<li data-track="15"><strong>反酸胀气</strong></li>
</ul>
<p data-track="16">如果胃部功能出现了问题，很容易伴随反酸胀气的情况，或许平时人们对于这种感觉并没有特别在意，吃完饭之后如果弯腰或者是有其他的剧烈活动，你感觉到有酸液逆流的状况，可能就是胃病的信号。</p>
<p data-track="17">所以如果出现了这种情况一定要提高警惕，千万不要任其发展。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-613" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/24c1bed1e416e0b6523dc49085beeac1.jpg" width="1000" height="634" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/24c1bed1e416e0b6523dc49085beeac1.jpg 1000w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/24c1bed1e416e0b6523dc49085beeac1-300x190.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/24c1bed1e416e0b6523dc49085beeac1-768x487.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="18">胃“喜欢”的4种水果，适量吃点或对胃好，胃也夸你聪明</h1>
<p data-track="19"><strong>1、樱桃</strong></p>
<p data-track="20">相信大家对于樱桃这种水果应该是不算陌生的，樱桃虽然个头不大，但是其中所含有的营养物质却非常丰富，饮食方面若能够适量吃点樱桃，可以为身体补充所需要的维生素，微量元素，矿物质元素等等，对于客户身体健康是有帮助的。</p>
<p data-track="21">那些外部功能不太好的人也可以适量吃点樱桃，或许有助于改善胃部不适的情况。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-614" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cb253adceb2829645ede24eafb8461ec-1024x642.jpg" width="1024" height="642" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cb253adceb2829645ede24eafb8461ec-1024x642.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cb253adceb2829645ede24eafb8461ec-300x188.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cb253adceb2829645ede24eafb8461ec-768x481.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cb253adceb2829645ede24eafb8461ec.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="22"><strong>2、苹果</strong></p>
<p data-track="23">俗话说一天一苹果，医生远离我，因为苹果这种水果一年四季都买得到，所以生活中人们对于苹果也不会特别在意，更是不怎么爱吃。</p>
<p data-track="24">苹果当中所含有的营养物质是非常丰富的，生活中若能够适量吃点苹果，或许也有助于减轻身体的负担，呵护身体健康，对于养护胃部也有帮助。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-615" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/52439a42c449e19710d2ab1731ba5d3c-1024x768.jpg" width="1024" height="768" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/52439a42c449e19710d2ab1731ba5d3c-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/52439a42c449e19710d2ab1731ba5d3c-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/52439a42c449e19710d2ab1731ba5d3c-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/52439a42c449e19710d2ab1731ba5d3c.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="25"><strong>3、菠萝</strong></p>
<p data-track="26">菠萝吃起来味道非常清新，而且营养价值也比较高，因为菠萝生长在热带地区受到光照时间比较长，所以其中的营养物质沉淀的要更加丰富。</p>
<p data-track="27">如果不行，外部功能受到伤害的话，生活中也可以考虑适量吃点菠萝，或许在一定程度上能够帮助减轻胃部的负担，对于呵护胃部健康有帮助。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-616" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9511202da9f3bc53aede6728baf69545-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9511202da9f3bc53aede6728baf69545-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9511202da9f3bc53aede6728baf69545-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9511202da9f3bc53aede6728baf69545-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9511202da9f3bc53aede6728baf69545.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="28"><strong>4、木瓜</strong></p>
<p data-track="29">木瓜同样也是一种比较典型的热带水果，这种水果的性质相对比较温和，而且营养价值也非常高，甚至木瓜有着“百益果王”的美誉。</p>
<p data-track="30">平时吃点木瓜对于呵护胃部健康也是有益处的，所以那些胃部功能本身就不太好的人可以考虑适量吃点木瓜，或许胃会夸你聪明。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-617" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9d22991e5ed03a2e807b6252244ca80a-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9d22991e5ed03a2e807b6252244ca80a-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9d22991e5ed03a2e807b6252244ca80a-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9d22991e5ed03a2e807b6252244ca80a-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/9d22991e5ed03a2e807b6252244ca80a.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="31">养护胃部，生活中要注意什么？</h1>
<p data-track="32"><strong>【注意保暖】</strong></p>
<p data-track="33">我们的胃部是一个喜温恶寒的器官，如果平时不注重保暖的话，那么就很有可能会导致外界的湿寒之气堆积在脾胃当中，不但会造成脾胃虚寒的情况，久而久之也可能会加重身体的负担。</p>
<p data-track="34">所以如果想要养护胃部的话，希望大家能够主动做好防寒保暖工作，比如寒冷的冬天，外出时要主动增减衣物。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-618" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/bfd0d257a7784fce699f8e8abb0211b3-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/bfd0d257a7784fce699f8e8abb0211b3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/bfd0d257a7784fce699f8e8abb0211b3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/bfd0d257a7784fce699f8e8abb0211b3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/bfd0d257a7784fce699f8e8abb0211b3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="35"><strong>【避免滥用药物】</strong></p>
<p data-track="36">现实生活中很多人存在滥用药物的情况，比如当感觉到身体不舒服的时候，人们可能并不会主动咨询医生，而是会根据以往的经验自己买点药物来吃。</p>
<p data-track="37">滥用药物也是一个伤害胃部的行为，因为药物主要依靠胃进行吸收，其中的一些副作用成分和刺激性成分，很有可能会影响到胃部的正常功能。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-619" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/1e20a1d75c034e6bf7fdd48aeeab52ee-1024x576.jpg" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/1e20a1d75c034e6bf7fdd48aeeab52ee-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/1e20a1d75c034e6bf7fdd48aeeab52ee-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/1e20a1d75c034e6bf7fdd48aeeab52ee-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/1e20a1d75c034e6bf7fdd48aeeab52ee.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="38"><strong>【远离烟酒】</strong></p>
<p data-track="39">吸烟喝酒是很多人都在做的一件事情，吸烟伤肺，喝酒伤肝，看起来跟胃没有太大的联系，但是在现场吸烟喝酒也会损伤其他的身体内脏，甚至是心血管的健康。</p>
<p data-track="40">所以如果经常吸烟喝酒的话，可能会给胃造成极大的负担和影响，并且也会导致胃黏膜受损。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-620" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/0a178fa2802e5029d5bcb5f67c59384b-1024x682.jpg" width="1024" height="682" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/0a178fa2802e5029d5bcb5f67c59384b-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/0a178fa2802e5029d5bcb5f67c59384b-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/0a178fa2802e5029d5bcb5f67c59384b-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/0a178fa2802e5029d5bcb5f67c59384b.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="41">胃部健康可能直接关乎着人的身体健康，所以希望大家在日常生活中能够积极调理和保养胃部，对此你还有其他需要补充的吗？欢迎在下方留言评论。</p>
